
PREREQUISITE:

Gambit-C Scheme programming system is available from:
http://dynamo.iro.umontreal.ca/wiki/index.php/Distributions

Note: Problem compiling with gambit version 4.7.* :
*** ERROR IN | list| -- Operator is not a PROCEDURE
(#!unbound
 '#(syntax-object fold ((top) #(ribcage #(fold) #((top)) #(fold))))
 '(global . fold)
 '*top*)

Please use gambit version 4.6.* for the moment. 


FDW enabled Postgres installation (at least 9.3):
http://www.postgresql.org/download/


COMPILATION:

You need to change this variables in the Makefile to suits you system:

GAMBITDIR = /opt/scheme/gambit/4.6.9
POSTGRESDIR = /opt/postgresql/9.3beta2

Then:
$ make clean all


